Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.22,0:00:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Dr. David Hawkins. I've been a physician for 35 years and specialized in the field of psychiatry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,For years I worked in the field of psychoanalysis and psychotherapy, various forms of psychotherapy and group therapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I did a lot of work on nutrition and its relationship to various bodily diseases, also emotional and mental disorders.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And for the last eight years I've been doing research into the nature of consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.24,0:00:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,exploring that domain which the world calls spiritual, elucidating the basic laws of self-healing,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,discovering what is common amongst all the people I know who have recovered from progressive, serious, fatal, even terminal illnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.59,0:01:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And so in this series, the Sedona series, we're talking about,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.09,0:01:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the utilization of the basic laws of mind and consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.91,0:01:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,in approaching such serious illnesses as AIDS, cancer, heart disease, hypertension, alcoholism, drug addiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.41,0:01:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them serious confronts, all of them things that require us to change our view of reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.27,0:01:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.79,0:01:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we'll be talking about body, mind, and spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.63,0:01:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be talking about the nature of consciousness in today's talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,which is addressed to patients with cancer, to families of people with cancer,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.23,0:01:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,to people who fear they might have cancer, to people who are in treatment with cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.59,0:01:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be talking about a holistic approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.35,0:01:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're not talking either-or.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not saying, well, you know, the treatment has to be traditional or an alternate treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.08,0:02:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What we're saying is and, to include in that larger dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.92,0:02:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Because true healing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,True healing requires the larger dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.28,0:02:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And all the people I know who've recovered from these chronic and very severe diseases,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.47,0:02:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,many of them who were given up as hopeless by their physicians in the medical community,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,have recovered and, without exception, they've all done so by exploring a greater definition of the truth of reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.07,0:02:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that which they are, exploring that realm of human knowledge called spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.18,0:02:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that relationship between body, mind, and spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, other than a catchphrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it something real that you can work with in everyday life and see actual results?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.28,0:02:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the friends that walk around who have recovered from all these fatal illnesses
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,are the walking evidence that we can all recover from any disease known to mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.81,0:03:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I, myself, as I have shared in other series and other talks in this series,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,had 15 or 20 aggressive illnesses, chronic, intractable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Although they were treatable, some of the symptoms were handled, the diseases did not get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.24,0:03:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, they were getting progressively worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So despite traditional medical treatment, I was merely holding the line on a few and losing the line on several.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And so it was exploring the greater dimension then, exploring those fields called consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.72,0:03:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and how they relate to self-healing, that a recovery from all of these illnesses, without exception,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,came about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.72,0:03:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The alteration in the blood chemistry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I once had gout in the high elevated uric acid level.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,After I learned that the body only does what is held in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I began to change what I was holding in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,then the body's chemistry literally began to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:04:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned that all the atoms and cells and elements, electrons,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,all of that which the body has made is conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But the cells of the body are conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is very important in the approaches that we'll be utilizing in the treatment of cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the relationship between body, mind, and spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He said the principle is that the body reflects that which is held in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And that which is held in mind reflects one's spiritual position.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.69,0:04:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And so it's necessary to know where all human experience takes place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if we address that level, we will be addressing the most powerful level.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If the physical is the consequence of the mental,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and the mental is the consequence of the spiritual,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.98,0:04:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,then it is in the area called consciousness itself that we should address ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And clinically this is so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,People who address that level, address the level of consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,watch transformations come about in their body
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,without even having addressed the body directly in any kind of a medical approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to know where experience is experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And let go some of the common illusions which people hold in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,just because they haven't looked into the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The body itself is incapable of experiencing itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, my hands as they are crossed here cannot experience themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They cannot experience their existence, their position in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.25,0:05:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the sensations have no capacity to experience themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of something greater than the physical body,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is what we call mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So that all the physical, and all that goes on with the physical body, sensations,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is experienced in the greater dimension called mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:05:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It is in mind that the experience of body takes place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.11,0:06:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind itself, curiously enough, has no capacity to experience itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A thought, for instance, a thought is just an energy form.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A thought has no capacity to experience its own thoughtness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A feeling has no capacity to experience its own feelingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,An emotion cannot be experienced,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,other than the fact that mind itself is held within an energy field that is greater than mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is the energy field of consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,which has no dimensions, which has no limitations,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and which has no form.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of consciousness that we are aware of what goes on in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And we know what's being registered in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,is because of that energy field called consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Even consciousness itself is not sufficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There is an energy field of a very high frequency in vibration,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.90,0:06:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the same as that of life itself, called awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.90,0:06:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It is out of awareness that there is the knowingness
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:07:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of what is going on within consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,which is reporting what is going on within mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,which in turn is reporting what is going on with the physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And so you can see the physical body itself is several levels removed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,from that which is the most real,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.48,0:07:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore the most powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We find that the energy of thought is far more powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,than the energy levels of the physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And so to understand some of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.18,0:07:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll need a context in which to understand the whole field of self-healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In a one hour talk today,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,we won't have time to cover the entire field.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have covered a number of things that have to be said
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.18,0:07:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,in other tapes in the consciousness series,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.18,0:07:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,where we did a tape, a talk on illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,we did another talk on health,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,we did another one on pain and suffering,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and there we pointed out that the two are not the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:07:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Suffering is one thing and pain is another,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,as I know because I just went to the dentist's last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And we did another one on stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be good to look at these if you can borrow them
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,or get them from somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,see where you can sort of expand your awareness of this whole field.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So today we're talking about, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the nature of consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,so that we create a context for ourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,so that the self-healing modalities that we will be describing later
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,will begin to make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,In the first place, how to hold that experience
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,of having a life-threatening illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,such as cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How to hold that? What to think of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.14,0:08:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we have two ways we can go
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,about it. We can go up or we can go down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Any kind of a confront, such as a death in the family,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.78,0:08:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,any kind of a serious illness or setback in a person's life,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,we always have that choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We can go down into feeling sorry for ourselves as victims,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:08:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,we can go down into self-pity, depression, despair,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,become suicidal,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.78,0:09:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,or we can see it as a challenge, as an opportunity,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,as a springboard to a greater awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Over and over these confronts come up in our lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,until we seize the opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and realize that this is the springboard to a greater awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the ordinary events in life don't have the power,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,they don't have the energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes max duress for a person to stop in their tracks
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and begin to question the realities of all the things
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that they have believed up to this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind will ordinarily not undertake
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the enormous energy expenditure
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.00,0:09:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of reorienting itself
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and getting a new different point of view about life
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and what is real,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,unless it has to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So this necessary growth, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,will only happen when we're up against a major confront.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.06,0:09:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So the way, the first thing to get about the cancer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:09:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,or the serious illness, whatever it may be,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,is that the purpose of this major confront
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,is for us to grow and to grow rapidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the first message.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Message number one is
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,it's time to grow,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.16,0:10:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and to grow as fast as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we have a certain time limit
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,with most of these fatal terminal illnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Things that the mind says are fatal and terminal
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,become fatal and terminal because of the power of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If the mind thinks that this is fatal and terminal,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.26,0:10:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,then it will be so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.26,0:10:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So we see now the beginning of the expression
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of the power of belief systems, belief systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, one of the main messages,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,we want to get across today,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is that no one needs to come or be victim
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of any illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And I count amongst my friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.26,0:10:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,people who have conquered every illness known to mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.26,0:10:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And the only reason I'm sitting before you today
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.26,0:10:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and able to make this talk
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is because I, myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,did exactly the same thing in my own personal life
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,where I would have hemorrhaged to death
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,from a variety of illnesses,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.26,0:11:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,all of which have remitted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.26,0:11:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All of which have remitted,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,including that I don't wear glasses anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.26,0:11:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,One time I wore bifocals and trifocals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Even vision itself went back to perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So that, that perfection which is held in mind then
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,reflects itself in the progressive perfection of the body
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.29,0:11:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and the letting go of this E.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to understand that the body itself
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.06,0:11:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,is expressing what is held in consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The body is merely an expression of the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.06,0:11:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The body is nothing but an expression
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.82,0:11:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which is held in consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a reflector of what we are holding consciously or unconsciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A person looks back in their mind and they'll say,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,well, I don't remember thinking about such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you don't remember thinking about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,find out if it's in your unconscious,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:12:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,all you have to do is look and see if it's in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So to help us create a different context,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.69,0:12:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,a way of looking at life,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.69,0:12:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,a way of looking at experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,a map from which we can understand
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,all the principles of self-healing,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.20,0:12:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,we have over here on the blackboard
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,outlined a chart of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,which we've utilized in other talks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you've seen some of the other tapes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,just realize that the person who is watching this again
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.52,0:12:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,is not the same person who saw it the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because every time we go over this,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,it's sort of like break-brain learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We learn it through familiarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The left brain is linear and logical
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and it gets things piecemeal sequentially.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The right brain circles over a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and by sheer exposure and familiarity,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.52,0:12:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,it just gets the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.52,0:12:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we'll be talking about today
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,are really things that in your unconscious,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.52,0:12:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,somewhere in the periphery of your mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you actually know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:13:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're going to try to pull them together,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,synchronize them in some kind of a useful way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.52,0:13:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So on the board we have,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,within this is called the box,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and everywhere I give talks,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,they often call it the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the human ego,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the self with a small s.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And that which people refer to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,when they say I or me, myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the self with a small s,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.19,0:13:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,is the human ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all that collection of concepts,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.19,0:13:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,impressions, opinions, feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.19,0:13:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,conscious and unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.19,0:13:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The totality of that that goes up to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,make up what the person means
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,when they say me, I, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And within the box you see
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,there are various levels of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And these are levels of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,starting at the very lowest
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and going up to the very highest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And they have all been calibrated,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.45,0:13:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,the research that we've done
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:13:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,with my co-workers, with Lorraine Ross.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.45,0:14:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What we did was we found out
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,the directions of the energy fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.45,0:14:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You see these energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,from courage on down
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,all go to the left,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,indicating that they have an anti-life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Destructive, do not support life,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,energy to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And all those from courage on up,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,you see the energy fields begin
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to swing to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.45,0:14:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And as we get closer and closer
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.45,0:14:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to the truth they become more powerfully
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.45,0:14:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And so then we notice that love
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.45,0:14:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,is way at the top of the scale
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and guilt, on the other hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,is way at the bottom of the scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Also they've been numerically calibrated
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,by some techniques which are very
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,complicated and difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and advanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And I won't go into the techniques
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,which is a science in itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But they can be confirmed by anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,who is familiar with kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The direction of the energy fields,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.38,0:14:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the calibrated numbers,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,their relative powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,can be reaffirmed by anybody
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,in their own living room
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.38,0:15:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,using just basics of kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And to learn about that I would recommend
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,a book by John Diamond called
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Life Energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It used to be called
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Behavioral Kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a way of testing out energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the relative powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and whether that thing is constructive
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.38,0:15:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,or destructive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.38,0:15:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Very helpful, for instance,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.38,0:15:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to test out medical treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You hold the medication in your hand
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and you have somebody test your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,will this medication be good for me or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If the medication is not good for you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,your arm will go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's good for you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,your arm will go strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.38,0:15:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So any kind of a treatment,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,even the doses,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.38,0:15:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you can test out and find out
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.38,0:15:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,what's good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's necessary then to know
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,something about energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,because this is intimately related
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to cancer and cancer research.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If we calibrate,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,if we say that death is zero,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,then we will discover that enlightenment,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.78,0:15:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to become a Buddha,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:15:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to become conscious of the absolute truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at about 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.78,0:16:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That energy field known as bliss,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.78,0:16:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,those energy fields known as
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,illumination or enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And then if we go down near the bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,of the box,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.33,0:16:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll see for instance that apathy,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,which calibrates at 50,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,has about half the energy of fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,which calibrates roughly at 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Grief at 75 has about half the energy of anger,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,which calibrates at 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.87,0:16:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Being neutral,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.87,0:16:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,that is to be detached or unattached,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,at 250 has only half the energy of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,which is at 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.42,0:16:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All these are extremely important.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.42,0:16:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because body, mind and spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,are actually all just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just being reflected in different planes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.44,0:16:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an artificial abstraction
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.44,0:16:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to cause body or mind or spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.44,0:16:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It is actually all the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.44,0:17:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All three are an expression of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore this energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,if it is a reversed or a negative energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.60,0:17:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is that negativity,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is destructive,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,destructive in all aspects of ourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,right down to the biochemical level.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.60,0:17:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So we see that the energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,which has a name to the right of the energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is expressed as a certain emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So if we want to know what our energy field is,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.60,0:17:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,all we have to do is look at what is the emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.60,0:17:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-pity, for instance,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically tells you what's happened with self-pity,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.60,0:17:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is that you are now in a negative energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,which calibrates at 50,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,which is weak indeed,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,as compared to love, which is 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The importance then we see immediately
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,of letting go of negative feelings and negative thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The negative energy of the feeling or the thought
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.94,0:17:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,transmits itself through the acupuncture energy system,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.94,0:18:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,through the 12 meridians,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.94,0:18:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,running down the body meridian,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.94,0:18:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and translates itself right into the energy of the body organ,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,right into the cells of the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I hate someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the cells of my body get the energy of hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And where is hate?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hate is right about here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.94,0:18:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a very reversed and quite powerful now,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.94,0:18:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,negative force.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.94,0:18:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,150 is a lot of power,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,twice as much power as 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Its power, therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,its capacity for destruction is greater.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.10,0:18:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So suppressed anger,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.10,0:18:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,suppressed anger then,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,has the capacity to change the energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,within the body's cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It has the power to actually change the programming
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,within the body's cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.81,0:18:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we are going to be talking about today
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.81,0:18:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is the enormous power that mind has
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.81,0:19:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,over every aspect of the body's functioning,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.81,0:19:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,right down to the smallest molecule, an atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been discovered that every atom is conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.81,0:19:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Every molecule within the body
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Every physiological and chemical transaction
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.81,0:19:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that goes on in the body
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.81,0:19:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is the result of a blueprint of that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.81,0:19:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,within consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.81,0:19:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them can be changed then
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,by changing consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I say that from personal experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.19,0:19:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,not only clinical experience
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and personal experience with friends and associates,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but of course with my own physical health.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I watched my own body chemistry
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,literally change
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,as I began to change
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.86,0:19:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,what I was holding about that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.86,0:19:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,within my mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.86,0:19:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,within my consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.86,0:19:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And I came upon that basic principle
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,essential to healing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.90,0:19:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,from all illnesses,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,because the same principles really apply
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to all illnesses,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that we are only subject to what we hold in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.02,0:20:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We are only subject to what we hold in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the mind's belief system
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.02,0:20:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that we give power to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that then manifests in the physical world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The physical body then
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is an expression
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which we've been holding in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.02,0:20:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we've either been holding it consciously
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.12,0:20:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,or unconsciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,See, people say,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.12,0:20:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,well I don't remember holding such a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there is what Jung calls
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the collective consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The thought form is there
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,within the collective consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And unconsciously
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.12,0:20:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,we can buy into,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.12,0:20:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,support,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.12,0:20:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,give energy to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.12,0:20:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,a negative belief system
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.12,0:20:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,without ever remembering it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.12,0:20:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,without consciously being aware of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.12,0:20:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly with cancer,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.86,0:20:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,we are dealing with something
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.86,0:20:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,which has been given
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,so much emotional energy
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.86,0:20:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,in the popular mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.86,0:20:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All the fear associated with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:20:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,all the negative connotations,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,all the thought forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, fear itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.86,0:21:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole fear unconsciously,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,this energy field here,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.86,0:21:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.86,0:21:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is a negative energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.86,0:21:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.86,0:21:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,if I am holding a lot of unconscious fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens is the fear now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.14,0:21:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,opens the door
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.14,0:21:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,to bring into my mind unconsciously
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.14,0:21:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,those things that are fearful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.14,0:21:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Those things that are fearful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,cancer falls into that which is fearful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And so therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.14,0:21:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,without ever having believed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that I am susceptible to cancer,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.14,0:21:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I may discover
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.14,0:21:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that it is occurring within the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.14,0:21:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that I have unwittingly bought in
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.14,0:21:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,to this collective belief system,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.14,0:21:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the collective thought form.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.14,0:21:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's just look at this field a little bit
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.17,0:21:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,because it will give us a better orientation
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.17,0:21:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to what we'll be talking about later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.17,0:21:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We see that at the very bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.20,0:21:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,is an energy field called guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.20,0:22:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It calibrates at 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.20,0:22:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It says death is zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.20,0:22:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, guilt is 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.20,0:22:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is the emotion that goes with guilt?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.20,0:22:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of self-hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.20,0:22:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And a great deal of research into this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.20,0:22:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,in psychology,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the psychosomatic viewpoints of cancers,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.20,0:22:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,reveals that there is a good deal
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.20,0:22:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,of unconscious self-hatred,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.20,0:22:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,self-condemnation,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.20,0:22:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,lack of acceptance of one's humanness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.20,0:22:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,at a deep level.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.20,0:22:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll talk about how to heal those things
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.20,0:22:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,because that's the way we bring about a healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We're interested in these talks in healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.20,0:22:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.30,0:22:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a difference between treating,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.30,0:22:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,curing, and healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.30,0:22:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible to treat an illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.39,0:22:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to treat symptoms,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.39,0:22:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to bring about an amelioration,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.39,0:22:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,a capacity, let's say, to live with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.39,0:22:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In the many years that I had migraine headaches,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.39,0:22:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I had duodenal ulcers, diverticulitis,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:22:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,gout, hypoglycemia,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.39,0:22:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,a whole variety of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.39,0:23:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I had vibration disease of the fingertips,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.39,0:23:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,threatening gangrene of the fingers and pillows and things.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.52,0:23:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Circulatory problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.52,0:23:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All of these illnesses, see,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.52,0:23:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,came about as a result of belief systems
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.52,0:23:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and they all were accompanied by
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.52,0:23:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,some degree of unconscious guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.52,0:23:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We find that unconscious guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.52,0:23:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,accompanies all illnesses
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.52,0:23:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what they may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.52,0:23:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have a physical illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.52,0:23:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you can just presume and you will be 100% right
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.52,0:23:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is unconscious guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.52,0:23:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and without the unconscious guilt,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.52,0:23:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,actually the disease cannot be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.52,0:23:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.52,0:23:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that which is,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.52,0:23:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,over on the right you'll see the process,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.52,0:23:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is destructive,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.52,0:23:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is accompanied by self-hatred,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.62,0:23:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,can only operate in a negative energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.62,0:23:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the secret of healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.62,0:23:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be like certain bacteria
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.65,0:23:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,will only grow in a culture media
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.65,0:23:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,under certain conditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.65,0:23:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,certain temperatures,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.65,0:24:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,certain amount of light and atmospheric conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.68,0:24:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you change the conditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.68,0:24:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the bacteria cannot live in that feature dish anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.68,0:24:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and they will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.68,0:24:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, that which is destructive,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.68,0:24:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that which meets the unconscious need
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.68,0:24:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,for the process of destruction,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.68,0:24:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,can only go on in an energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.68,0:24:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,which itself is negative
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.84,0:24:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and allows the negative energy of destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.84,0:24:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to take place.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.00,0:24:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that starts to give us a clue
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.00,0:24:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to that which heals.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.00,0:24:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That which the energy field goes to the right
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.00,0:24:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,in nature,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.29,0:24:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,in nature you see the rotation of an energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.29,0:24:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is all decisive.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.35,0:24:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, a drug,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.35,0:24:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the chemical effect of a molecule
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.35,0:24:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is totally dependent on whether it spins to the right
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.35,0:24:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,or it spins to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.35,0:24:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take dextroamphetamine sulfate as an example.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.35,0:24:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Dextro meaning to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.35,0:24:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Dextroamphetamine sulfate is so-called speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.35,0:25:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And everybody is familiar in our culture
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.35,0:25:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,with what the effect of speed is.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.35,0:25:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Weight loss and the feeling of high excitability,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.35,0:25:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,grinding your teeth and finally manic attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.35,0:25:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Revolve, meaning to the left,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.93,0:25:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,amphetamine sulfate has no such effect whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.93,0:25:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same molecule
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.93,0:25:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but the rotation is in the opposite direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.93,0:25:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So the rotation of an energy field then,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.31,0:25:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,these are nurturing
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.31,0:25:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and will support life and healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.31,0:25:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,These on the left are destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.31,0:25:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore that which is destructive
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.31,0:25:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,must take place in a negative energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.31,0:25:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, all you need to do to heal yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.31,0:25:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,is to move from the negative energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.31,0:25:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,into a positive energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.31,0:25:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-healing is so simple, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.31,0:25:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really, that's what it amounts to.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.31,0:25:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What it amounts to is changing the predominant energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.31,0:25:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,within your consciousness from negative to positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.31,0:25:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the question arises of how do you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.31,0:25:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you see the physics of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.31,0:26:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the science of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.31,0:26:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the metaphysics of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.31,0:26:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.31,0:26:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the emotional truth of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.31,0:26:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,from medical, psychiatric,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.31,0:26:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,holistic viewpoints,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.31,0:26:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you see why we should let go of these emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.31,0:26:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in order to become a goody-goody person,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.31,0:26:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but frankly because to hang on to them will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.31,0:26:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All these things are,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.43,0:26:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,we mentioned kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.43,0:26:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,See, with kinesiology you test somebody's strength
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.43,0:26:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and they hold any thought
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.43,0:26:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,that has to do with any of these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.43,0:26:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Something you feel guilty about,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.43,0:26:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,something you feel hopeless about,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.43,0:26:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,something you're sad and grieving about,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.43,0:26:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,something you're afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.43,0:26:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Something that you're into wanting and desiring,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.43,0:26:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,something you're angry about,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.43,0:26:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,something you're prideful about.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.43,0:26:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Some truth that you're denying,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.43,0:26:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,some worry, some craving,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.43,0:26:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,some regret, some loss,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.69,0:26:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,some form of self-hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.69,0:26:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And any time you do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.85,0:26:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the body instantly goes weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.85,0:26:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And when it goes weak,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.85,0:27:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,it means you just blew your acupuncture system.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.85,0:27:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It just means you blew the meridian
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.85,0:27:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to the various bodily organs.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.85,0:27:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It means that you just changed the chemical pattern,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.85,0:27:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the reproductive pattern,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.85,0:27:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're tearing up the cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.46,0:27:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's obvious that all we have to do to heal anything
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.46,0:27:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is to move out of a negative energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.46,0:27:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and into a positive energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.46,0:27:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the power of the healing increases.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.46,0:27:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The higher, the more positive the energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.46,0:27:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why the holistic approaches have worked
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.46,0:27:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,where medical science has not been able to affect the cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.46,0:27:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And I myself, as I said, am a living example.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.46,0:27:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Without knowing what I'm talking about today,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.46,0:27:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be here to give this lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.46,0:27:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have died, for instance,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.46,0:27:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,22 and a half years ago of another disease
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.46,0:27:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,which preceded all the other ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.46,0:27:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A fatal progressive disease
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.46,0:27:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,which reversed itself right at the point of death itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.46,0:27:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So guilt is the most injurious, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.10,0:27:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's accompanied by self-hatred
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.10,0:27:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and the process that it brings in
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.10,0:28:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,is automatically destructive.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.10,0:28:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And we know that from the study of geomancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.10,0:28:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Geomancy is the study of energy fields in nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.10,0:28:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we study the effect of energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.10,0:28:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,in nature, we will find that a negative energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.10,0:28:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,in nature is anti-life.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.10,0:28:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It does not support life.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.10,0:28:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So if a canyon, the energy field in that canyon,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.10,0:28:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,if it goes into a negative direction
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.10,0:28:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,for a variety of reasons,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.10,0:28:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,if the crossing of the ley line,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.10,0:28:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the cutting, like I know the situation where a dam
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.10,0:28:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,cut the ley line, reversed the energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.10,0:28:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,now the lives of everyone along that ley line
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.10,0:28:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,were influenced in a negative direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.10,0:28:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, in a way, you see it's impersonal.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.10,0:28:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This energy field then has a destructive effect
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.10,0:28:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,within nature itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.10,0:28:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And because you are part of nature,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.10,0:28:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,then you have to suffer the loss
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.10,0:28:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that comes out of that destructive quality
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.54,0:28:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,of the energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.54,0:28:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So, obviously then, letting go of guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.54,0:28:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and letting go of unconscious guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.54,0:29:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,is crucial to recovering from any serious disease,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.54,0:29:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,especially cancer, where lack of self-esteem
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.54,0:29:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and self-hatred and fear play such a predominant part
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.54,0:29:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and the next energy field above this
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.64,0:29:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to be accompanied by hopelessness and despair
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.64,0:29:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is called apathy, which is an energy field of 50
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.64,0:29:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and the world view, the view of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.64,0:29:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that comes out of that is one of hopelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.64,0:29:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,To fall into self-pity and hopelessness then
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.64,0:29:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is to allow yourself to be overtaken
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.64,0:29:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and become victim of an energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.64,0:29:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,which favors the progression of the cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.64,0:29:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So what about that is grief?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.18,0:29:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, when people first get a cancer,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.18,0:29:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll have a diagnosis,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.18,0:29:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,especially if they're a younger person.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.18,0:29:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They will say, why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.18,0:29:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And go into regret, a feeling of loss and despondency.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.18,0:29:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The world now begins to look sad, life looks sad,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.18,0:29:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and they can then become the victim of this energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.18,0:30:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep repeating energy field because I want you to see
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.18,0:30:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,your own innocence in this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.18,0:30:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of your own innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.18,0:30:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that you literally allow yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.18,0:30:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to be run by this energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.18,0:30:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The stage above that, the one
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.18,0:30:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that's also very prevalent
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.18,0:30:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,in patients who develop cancer is fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.18,0:30:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, fear with a very negative energy
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.18,0:30:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,has more power now, an energy field of 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.18,0:30:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The world looks frightening, life looks frightening,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.18,0:30:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and God begins to look almost punitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.18,0:30:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of a God is it that could give you cancer, etc.?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.18,0:30:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And the process of life itself begins to feel deflated.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.18,0:30:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The person is tempted to become dispirited,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.18,0:30:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,de-energized, and give in to the destructiveness,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.73,0:30:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to allow the thing to progress, unconsciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.73,0:30:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can begin to desire something better for yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.73,0:30:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,than being the victim, being the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.73,0:30:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All the people I know recovered from all these illnesses
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.73,0:30:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,did not settle for being victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.73,0:31:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They all began to desire something better for themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.73,0:31:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.73,0:31:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And they began to research and began to look outside
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.73,0:31:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,of this traditional medical model.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.73,0:31:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.73,0:31:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They said, Doctor, well, is that all it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.73,0:31:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, is that all you got to offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.73,0:31:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's going to take more than that to heal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.73,0:31:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And they began to find out,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.73,0:31:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is there something else that can heal it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.73,0:31:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So out of that desire, out of the anger at being victim,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.73,0:31:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,see, we can use the energy fields of these emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.73,0:31:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,in a constructive way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.73,0:31:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can use the energy fields of anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.14,0:31:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost my own stepdaughter, you know, years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.14,0:31:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,from Hodgkin's disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.14,0:31:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember her going through
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.14,0:31:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.14,0:31:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Being angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.14,0:31:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Angry enough to begin to investigate and research
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.14,0:31:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and see what can be done about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.14,0:31:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Angriness.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.14,0:31:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So the anger can be used constructively.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.14,0:31:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The anger, I don't have to be victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.14,0:31:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to give in to this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.14,0:32:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And to begin to take pride in our ability
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.14,0:32:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,to expand our own consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.14,0:32:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer, as you look into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.14,0:32:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,is there more that can be done?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.14,0:32:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, it is yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.14,0:32:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin to take pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.14,0:32:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, to move up to a very decisive point
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.14,0:32:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,called courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.14,0:32:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, what happens at courage,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.27,0:32:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,not only does the energy field go all the way up to 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.27,0:32:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,which is twice the energy of fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.27,0:32:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,twice the energy of fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.27,0:32:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but what is more important
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.27,0:32:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is that the direction of the energy field has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.27,0:32:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone from negative,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.27,0:32:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,from a field which supports that which is destructive,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.27,0:32:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and it has suddenly now gone neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.30,0:32:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, these energy fields down here are like an antenna.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.30,0:32:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They're like an antenna tuned to the negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.30,0:32:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So the energy field which surrounds the human body
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.30,0:32:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is like an antenna.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.82,0:32:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And when it's tuned to the negative,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.82,0:32:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,it draws to itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.82,0:32:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It draws to itself that which is destructive.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.82,0:32:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And the body, of course, is right in the way
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.82,0:32:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,of that destructive energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.82,0:33:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and gets hit by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.82,0:33:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of the negativity,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.82,0:33:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the destructiveness expressing itself through the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.82,0:33:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,hitting the body, expressing itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.82,0:33:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And in this particular case of cancer,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.82,0:33:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,it draws our attention to the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.82,0:33:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is some error involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.82,0:33:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There is some error.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.82,0:33:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The courage to begin to look and see
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.82,0:33:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is perhaps some error.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.82,0:33:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The way I've been holding life,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.82,0:33:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the way I've been holding my belief system,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.42,0:33:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the way I think about myself
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.42,0:33:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,perhaps has been an error.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.42,0:33:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So one of the things about this level here of courage
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.42,0:33:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is the beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.42,0:33:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the beginning, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.42,0:33:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,of knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.42,0:33:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Our expression of that is humility.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.42,0:33:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Courage is expressed by humility.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.42,0:33:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And now the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.42,0:33:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,our view of the world begins to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.42,0:33:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of hopeless, out of sad,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.42,0:33:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,out of frightened, out of frustrating,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.42,0:33:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,out of competitive,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.68,0:34:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,out of opportunistic and status.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.16,0:34:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It suddenly moves up to a world of opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.61,0:34:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So the doors begin to open.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.61,0:34:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Below this, the mind is closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.61,0:34:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It thinks it knows the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.61,0:34:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It thinks it knows the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.61,0:34:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we have the courage,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.61,0:34:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens is the mind begins to open.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.61,0:34:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And it says,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.61,0:34:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet there's answers I don't even know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.61,0:34:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I don't even know the right questions to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.61,0:34:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And the minute we begin to open ourselves up,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.61,0:34:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens is we become empowered.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.61,0:34:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,See the process over on the right,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.61,0:34:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,when we have the courage to have an open mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.61,0:34:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is when we become empowered.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.61,0:34:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So below this, these are all states of powerlessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.61,0:34:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All states of victimhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.61,0:34:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we move up to an energy field of 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.61,0:34:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the capacity to face the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.61,0:34:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and begin to take responsibility for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.61,0:34:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,See, the thing about victim
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.61,0:34:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is victim doesn't take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.61,0:34:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Victim says, well, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.06,0:35:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason I got this is because of the bacteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.06,0:35:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And the reason I got this is because of the virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.06,0:35:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I got this is because of the cancer cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.06,0:35:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always something outside of oneself,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.06,0:35:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,outside of one's consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.06,0:35:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That one is the victim of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.06,0:35:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No one begins to own that I've had something to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.06,0:35:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.06,0:35:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,is the result of something that I've been holding in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.06,0:35:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The situation right above courage
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.30,0:35:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is a level called neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.30,0:35:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So see, at neutral, the arrow has now gone to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.30,0:35:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And the energy field has jumped up to 250.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.30,0:35:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The emotional state of that is called detached or non-attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.30,0:35:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The process going on in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.37,0:36:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,is one of being released.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.37,0:36:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,One experiences the okayness of life
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.37,0:36:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and experiences a new and greater freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.37,0:36:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And that would be expressed, let's say,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.37,0:36:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,in serious illnesses or serious situations
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.37,0:36:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,because all serious situations,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.37,0:36:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,see, call forth the same need
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.37,0:36:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,to confront truth within yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.37,0:36:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and ascertain what is your position about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.69,0:36:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be expressed, let's say, as fatalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.91,0:36:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Fatalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.91,0:36:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea that we had during the war,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.91,0:36:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say, when I was in World War II.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.91,0:36:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea that the bullet, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.91,0:36:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,that's meant for you has your name on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.91,0:36:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's no point of being afraid of bullets
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.91,0:36:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,because if it hasn't got your name on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.91,0:36:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not going to hit you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.91,0:36:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That can be expressed as karma, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.91,0:36:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And whatever is going to be is destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.91,0:36:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Karma is the way it's supposed to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.91,0:36:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So the fatalistic position
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.91,0:36:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,is a certain peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.91,0:36:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A certain peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.91,0:37:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We are detached.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.91,0:37:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So the person with cancer who reaches that says,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.91,0:37:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,well, look, if I survive, I survive,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.91,0:37:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and if I don't, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.91,0:37:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.91,0:37:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing the best I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.91,0:37:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If I make it, I make it,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.91,0:37:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and if I don't, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.91,0:37:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm prepared to go in either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.91,0:37:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So that is certainly a far more comfortable position,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.91,0:37:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, than to be in grief about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.91,0:37:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,self-pity, anger, resentment, arrogance, denial.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.91,0:37:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,People go into denial
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.91,0:37:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and deny they have the cancer, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.91,0:37:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They will come up with a thought
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.91,0:37:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's been cured and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.26,0:37:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Without having gone through the necessary work
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.26,0:37:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to bring about, bring that about
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.26,0:37:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,as a reality in their life.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.26,0:37:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's sort of magical thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.71,0:37:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We can move above that to a willingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.71,0:37:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,a friendly view of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.71,0:37:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,where we see life is promising and hopeful,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.71,0:37:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and we discover, yes, there are answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.78,0:37:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, there are answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.78,0:37:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There are lots of people walking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.78,0:37:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We have had terminal, fatal,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.78,0:38:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,given up all hope diseases of all kinds,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.78,0:38:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,including cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.87,0:38:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happened here is we've introduced intention,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.87,0:38:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,increased one's power,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.87,0:38:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,increased one's power,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.87,0:38:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,up to accepting the fact that, yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.87,0:38:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,you can let go of this illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.87,0:38:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and there are healing modalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.87,0:38:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our harmonious world
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.87,0:38:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,in which there are lots of people
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.87,0:38:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,who have recovered from these illnesses
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.87,0:38:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,who are only too happy to share with you
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.87,0:38:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the truths that they have discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.87,0:38:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Because they experience God
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.87,0:38:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,as that which is merciful.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.87,0:38:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The people at the bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.87,0:38:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,experience God as punitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.87,0:38:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And even if they don't believe in God,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.87,0:38:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,they believe in self-punishment
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.87,0:38:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,in one form or another,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.87,0:38:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,or pain and suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.87,0:38:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And feeling adequate, feeling confident,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.87,0:38:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,yes, that there is an answer,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.87,0:38:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,begins a transformation of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.87,0:38:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It moves us up to the willingness to be coming
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.87,0:38:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,into this energy field called love.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.87,0:38:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a crucial level because
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.87,0:38:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy field of love is the one that heals.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.87,0:39:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All those organizations of people
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.58,0:39:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,who are very famous for their capacity to heal,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.58,0:39:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Alcoholics Anonymous being probably
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.58,0:39:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the most famous on the planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.58,0:39:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,hopeless, progressive, chronic,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.58,0:39:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,intractable disease,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.58,0:39:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,for which there is no answer,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.58,0:39:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and medicine admitted
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.61,0:39:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is no cure for the condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.61,0:39:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, here is an incurable, progressive,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.61,0:39:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,disease that destroys every organ of the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.61,0:39:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,including sanity itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.61,0:39:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And we know there are half a million people
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.61,0:39:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,walking around who have totally
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.61,0:39:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and 100% recovered from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.61,0:39:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, their lives have been transformed
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.64,0:39:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,because there again, the affliction
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.64,0:39:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,was used as a springboard
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.64,0:39:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to a greater consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.64,0:39:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and a greater awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.64,0:39:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,To move into a commitment
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.64,0:39:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to that which is loving.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.64,0:39:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And we said the nature of it is unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.64,0:39:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the conditional love of
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.64,0:39:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I will love you if you will do this
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.64,0:40:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,or you will do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.67,0:40:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,To move into this begins a process
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.67,0:40:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,called revelation.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.67,0:40:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It begins the release within the mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.67,0:40:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,within the brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.67,0:40:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,of certain chemicals we call endorphins.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.02,0:40:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So, all these energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.02,0:40:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,have within the mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.02,0:40:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,have within the brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.02,0:40:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,concomitant changes in the enzymes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.02,0:40:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There are neurotransmitter changes
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.02,0:40:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,there is the release of whole,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.02,0:40:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,opening of whole banks of neurons.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.02,0:40:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So therefore, the person
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.18,0:40:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,has moved into lovingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.18,0:40:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,which is a healing energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.18,0:40:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,has at their disposal
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.18,0:40:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the utilization of millions
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.18,0:40:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and millions of neurons
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.18,0:40:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,which people who are
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.18,0:40:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,in a negative emotional state
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.18,0:40:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,do not have at their fingertips.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.18,0:40:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, they have assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.82,0:40:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So to move into the energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.82,0:40:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,of unconditional love then
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.82,0:40:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,starts the healing process
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.82,0:40:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,going.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.50,0:41:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that when we calibrated
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.50,0:41:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,we found that the healing
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.69,0:41:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,healing occurs in an energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.69,0:41:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,which you calibrate at about 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.69,0:41:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.26,0:41:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.26,0:41:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So how do we bring about
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.26,0:41:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the self-healing then?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.26,0:41:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we have to let go
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.26,0:41:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of a number of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.26,0:41:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to let go of unconscious guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.26,0:41:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to discover,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.26,0:41:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,how can I unearth that
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.26,0:41:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,which I feel guilty about?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.26,0:41:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We begin a self-questioning process.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.26,0:41:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.26,0:41:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the person is fearful.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.26,0:41:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They say, well, even if it
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.26,0:41:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,would heal my cancer,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.26,0:41:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I can't do that
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.26,0:41:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,because if I start opening Pandora's box
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.26,0:41:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be swamped
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.26,0:41:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,by all the negativity and the guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.26,0:41:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that I have suppressed and repressed
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.26,0:41:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and pushed out of awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.26,0:41:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,all my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.33,0:41:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we need some kind of tools,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.33,0:41:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,some kind of a practical way
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.33,0:41:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to process these things
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.35,0:42:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and to begin with,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.35,0:42:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,we need a context,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.35,0:42:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,a way in which to hold
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.35,0:42:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,all that comes up
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.35,0:42:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,in this self-investigative process.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.35,0:42:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore we need a tool,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.35,0:42:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the realization of what has been
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.35,0:42:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the basis of all our behavior
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.35,0:42:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,all of our life.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.64,0:42:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A context, a way to hold that
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.64,0:42:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,so that as it comes up,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.64,0:42:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the guilt is automatically wiped out
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.64,0:42:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,by a higher understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.02,0:42:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to realize that
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.02,0:42:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,we've committed exactly one sin,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.02,0:42:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the word in quotes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.02,0:42:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We have been committing exactly one sin
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.02,0:42:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout our life,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.02,0:42:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's the same sin over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.02,0:42:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is that everything we ever did,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.02,0:42:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,our intentions and our purposes,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.02,0:42:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,was coming out
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.02,0:42:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,of the thought that
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.02,0:42:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,this will bring about happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.02,0:42:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very important to know this,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.02,0:42:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to realize that the reason
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.06,0:42:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,we did what we did at the time
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.06,0:42:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,is because we thought that
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.06,0:42:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that was necessary for our survival
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.06,0:42:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and our survival was necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.06,0:43:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,for our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.06,0:43:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And so everything we did,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.06,0:43:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,we did in the name of
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.06,0:43:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the innocent thought
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.18,0:43:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that this will bring us happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.18,0:43:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanting happiness is the basic
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.18,0:43:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,of all human emotions, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.34,0:43:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, the basic premise,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.34,0:43:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the most primitive illusion of all
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.34,0:43:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is that it is the body
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.34,0:43:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that is the source of my happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.34,0:43:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore the fear of death
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.34,0:43:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is really, if I lose the body
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.34,0:43:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I will lose the source of happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.34,0:43:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I will lose consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.50,0:43:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,People who are spiritually aware,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.50,0:43:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of course this is nonsense,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.50,0:43:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,because they no longer identify
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.50,0:43:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,with the physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.50,0:43:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If I am awareness,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.50,0:43:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,if I am consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.50,0:43:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,out of which comes a knowingness
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.50,0:43:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of what is happening within mind
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.50,0:43:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and within body,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.50,0:43:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,then body is the bottom rung
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.50,0:43:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,on the ladder, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.50,0:43:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness is totally unaffected
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.50,0:43:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,about what it is conscious of.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.50,0:43:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So we need to let go
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.50,0:43:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of these negative emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.50,0:44:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and let go of suppressing them
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.50,0:44:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and repressing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.50,0:44:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And we have to have a tool to do that
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.50,0:44:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is to let go of resisting them
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.50,0:44:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,as they come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.86,0:44:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to keep our eye on the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.86,0:44:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that consciousness innately within itself
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.86,0:44:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,is innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.95,0:44:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The nature of consciousness itself
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.95,0:44:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,is the innocence of the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.95,0:44:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How did we begin to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.78,0:44:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the things that we began to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.78,0:44:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,as we grew older?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.78,0:44:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We look at the child and we see
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.78,0:44:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,how innocent and trusting it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.78,0:44:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It is completely lacking in guile.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.78,0:44:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that its motivations
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.78,0:44:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,are pure, in at least our understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.78,0:44:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,of purity.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.58,0:44:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How does that later become
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.58,0:44:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the consciousness of the adult?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.58,0:44:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because the program
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.58,0:44:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,that the child buys
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.58,0:44:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and buys into,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.74,0:44:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact that it's programmable
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.74,0:44:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,is coming out of the very nature
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.74,0:44:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,of innocence itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.74,0:44:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because the child is innocent
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.74,0:44:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and trusting that it begins
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.74,0:45:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to buy and believe everything
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.74,0:45:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that it hears,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.74,0:45:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,including all the thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.74,0:45:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that later express themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.74,0:45:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,as cancer having to do
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.74,0:45:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,with self-condemnation,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.90,0:45:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,fearful thoughts,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.90,0:45:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,thoughts of rejecting oneself
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.90,0:45:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and its expression of its humanness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.90,0:45:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And so to heal cancer then
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.90,0:45:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,we need an approach,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.90,0:45:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,a willingness to heal ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.90,0:45:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,by means of compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.90,0:45:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,To come from compassion,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.90,0:45:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that is our greater,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.90,0:45:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,our higher self,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.90,0:45:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,understanding that out of innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.90,0:45:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,all these belief systems came about.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.90,0:45:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And how does the belief system
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.90,0:45:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,express itself in daily life?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.90,0:45:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It expressed itself as the thought
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.90,0:45:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that if I do this
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.90,0:45:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,or I have that,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.90,0:45:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,then I will be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.90,0:45:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And so does,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.90,0:45:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,how does grief or loss
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.90,0:45:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,affect us?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.97,0:45:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason it affects us
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.97,0:45:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is we thought that was going to be
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.97,0:45:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,a source of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.97,0:46:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we're regretting is what we see
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.97,0:46:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,when we're angry
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.97,0:46:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,because some obstacle
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.97,0:46:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,stands between
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.97,0:46:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the way of ourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.97,0:46:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,our intentions,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.97,0:46:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,what we want,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.19,0:46:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and that which we consider
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.19,0:46:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to be the source of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.19,0:46:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So if we go back to the board here,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.19,0:46:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,we ask what is the illusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.19,0:46:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the illusion
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.19,0:46:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that was held in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.19,0:46:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,now expressing itself in the form of cancer?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.19,0:46:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And the illusion was
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.19,0:46:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,all these levels from courage on down,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.19,0:46:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,growth,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.19,0:46:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,we all thought that the source of happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.19,0:46:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,was something outside of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.38,0:46:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That something outside of myself
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.38,0:46:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,has the power
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.38,0:46:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to make me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.38,0:46:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute I give away my power
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.38,0:46:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and project it outside of myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.38,0:46:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I put myself in a negative energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.38,0:46:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I set myself up
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.38,0:46:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,as a victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.12,0:46:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the unconscious purpose of the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.12,0:46:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,is to prove that you are a victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.12,0:47:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And the test of cancer
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.12,0:47:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,is the test of whether or not
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.12,0:47:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,you will continue
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.12,0:47:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to go along with this
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.12,0:47:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and buy into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.50,0:47:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,95% of the world does.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.50,0:47:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm talking to today
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.50,0:47:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,are the 5% of the people
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.50,0:47:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,who are willing to wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.50,0:47:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and become conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.50,0:47:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,95% of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.50,0:47:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you see the ego would rather be right
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.50,0:47:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and have you dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.60,0:47:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego would rather be right
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.60,0:47:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,even if it costs you your life
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.60,0:47:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than give up the position
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.60,0:47:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that I am the innocent victim
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.60,0:47:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,or something outside of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.40,0:47:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you see your true innocence,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.40,0:47:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,then you don't need
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.40,0:47:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the pseudo-innocence of victimhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.40,0:47:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,See, the owning of true innocence,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.50,0:47:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't need
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.50,0:47:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the pseudo-innocence of victimhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.50,0:47:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Inasmuch as there is no victim,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.50,0:47:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,there was only a belief system
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.66,0:47:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,in the first place
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.66,0:47:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,which we kicked up out of our innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.66,0:47:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The thought, for instance,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.23,0:48:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that success brings us happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.23,0:48:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is probably the most notorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.23,0:48:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,As every middle-aged business man
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.23,0:48:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,who has become successful knows,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.23,0:48:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,what he gets out of his success
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.23,0:48:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is a daily headache and exhaustion
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.23,0:48:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and a number of lawsuits
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.23,0:48:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and some greed and envy
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.23,0:48:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,from his colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.23,0:48:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He says to himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.23,0:48:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,where is all the happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.23,0:48:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that success was supposed to bring me?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.23,0:48:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's brought me some pleasures,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.23,0:48:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,a nice car, a nice apartment,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.23,0:48:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,a nice address, and nice clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.23,0:48:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But those things are not happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.23,0:48:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,because worldly success
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.23,0:48:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is an energy field of about
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.23,0:48:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,120.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.23,0:48:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So worldly success
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.23,0:48:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,does not bring about the thing
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.23,0:48:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore the disillusionment
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.23,0:48:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and the feeling of guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.23,0:48:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How does the guilt come about?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.23,0:48:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The guilt comes about
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.23,0:48:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,as a result of feeling that
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.23,0:48:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,we have sold ourselves out subtly,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.23,0:48:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that we have sold out
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.33,0:48:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth about ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.33,0:48:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So to recover from cancer
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.33,0:49:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,or any other illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.33,0:49:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,we have to reconnect
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.33,0:49:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,with our own intrinsic innocence,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.33,0:49:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,which has been totally unaffected
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.33,0:49:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,by all of life's events,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.33,0:49:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,to reown that level of awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.33,0:49:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,of self,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.33,0:49:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,which is beyond all worldly events.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.33,0:49:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Something within us remains the same
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.33,0:49:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what is going on
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.33,0:49:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,in our life experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.33,0:49:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Something has been unchanged.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.33,0:49:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something that wakes up
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.33,0:49:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the first thing in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.33,0:49:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, before you realize where you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.33,0:49:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,before you realize what day it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.33,0:49:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,before you realize what it is
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.49,0:49:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,you're supposed to do today.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.49,0:49:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When you wake up into that state of awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.49,0:49:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,you are much closer to the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.49,0:49:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,of your own higher self
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.49,0:49:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and you will realize it is totally unaffected,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.49,0:49:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,it is beyond all of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.49,0:49:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only when your consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.49,0:49:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,comes down,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.49,0:49:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,comes down into the world
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.49,0:49:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,of concrete thought
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.87,0:49:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,you say, oh yes, it's Monday
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.87,0:49:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and oh yes, I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.87,0:49:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're coming down into the level
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.87,0:50:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,of concrete thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.94,0:50:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You are really leaving
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.94,0:50:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,being closed to the truth of that
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.94,0:50:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,which is beyond all of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.94,0:50:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So we re-own then
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.06,0:50:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.06,0:50:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to decide what our position will be
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.06,0:50:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,about life's events.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.06,0:50:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Those things which bring about
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.06,0:50:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,extreme duress.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.54,0:50:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We can become victims
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.54,0:50:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,or we can see it as a springboard
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.54,0:50:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to transcending that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.38,0:50:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The first thing we have to let go of
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.38,0:50:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,is unconscious guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.38,0:50:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why something like
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.38,0:50:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The Course of Miracles
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.38,0:50:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,which has become very famous
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.38,0:50:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,in the state in which I live,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.38,0:50:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,in which I live now.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.38,0:50:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a day which is
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.41,0:50:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgiveness Day
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.41,0:50:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's taken directly out of The Course of Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.14,0:50:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The Course of Miracles is a teaching
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.14,0:50:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,of love and forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.14,0:50:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and the letting go of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.14,0:50:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And many of the people I know
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.14,0:50:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,who've recovered from cancer
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.14,0:51:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and multiple sclerosis
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.14,0:51:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and other serious debilitating illnesses
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.14,0:51:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,have done so as a result
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.14,0:51:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,of this particular
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.14,0:51:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,or other courses which are similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.14,0:51:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They are designed to show us
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.14,0:51:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,how to change our point of view
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.14,0:51:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and how to let go of condemnation
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.14,0:51:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,of ourselves and others.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.14,0:51:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How to let go of guilt and fear
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.14,0:51:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and how to move ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.14,0:51:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,into the willingness to be loving
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.14,0:51:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and forgiving and compassionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.14,0:51:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of that comes the desire to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.14,0:51:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So in our self-healing then
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.37,0:51:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,we need to almost like
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.37,0:51:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,take ourselves in our own arms
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.56,0:51:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,become that which is compassionate
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.56,0:51:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and healing
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.56,0:51:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,because all of us have the healer
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.56,0:51:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,all of us have within us the healer
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.56,0:51:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and we begin now
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.56,0:51:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to heal our humanness.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.56,0:51:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.72,0:51:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we get rid of the ego?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.72,0:51:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Not by making it an enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.72,0:51:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,not by trying to attack it
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.72,0:51:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,not by getting into an adversary position
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.72,0:51:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,with it
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.72,0:51:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but by loving it out of existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.72,0:52:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We literally dissolve the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.72,0:52:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,through compassion and love
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.72,0:52:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.04,0:52:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When you see that anything
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.04,0:52:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you've ever done in your lifetime
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.04,0:52:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,when you can really see that
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.04,0:52:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,when your main intention
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.42,0:52:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is to understand it
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.42,0:52:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so that out of compassion it becomes healed
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.42,0:52:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,when we do this with other people
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.42,0:52:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,when we let go of the desire to be judgmental
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.42,0:52:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,towards ourselves and towards other people
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.42,0:52:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,then what happens is
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.42,0:52:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,our own energy field begins to move
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.42,0:52:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,in a positive direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.42,0:52:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,See, cancer cannot grow
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.42,0:52:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,in a positive energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.42,0:52:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,it can only grow in a negative energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.42,0:52:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we look over here
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.42,0:52:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,we see that love
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.42,0:52:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is the one that's available
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.42,0:52:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.42,0:52:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The commitment to unconditional love
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.42,0:52:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,what is that kind of love?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.42,0:52:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.42,0:52:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hollywood style emotionalism
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.42,0:52:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that sentimentality
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.42,0:52:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that attachment, that dependency
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.42,0:52:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that mutual control back and forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.42,0:52:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead we're talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.42,0:53:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,an intention
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.42,0:53:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that's described as lovingness
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.42,0:53:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to commit oneself
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.42,0:53:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to nurture and support
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.42,0:53:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,all of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.42,0:53:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what it's expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.42,0:53:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what it's expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.42,0:53:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,See, when you think about it
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.42,0:53:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,life flows equally
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.42,0:53:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,into the saint
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.42,0:53:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and into the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.42,0:53:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Life is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.42,0:53:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is the God within
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.42,0:53:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,makes no judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.42,0:53:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It flows equally into all.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.42,0:53:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And as it says in the scripture
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.42,0:53:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the rain falls equally on all.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.42,0:53:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,To move out of judgmentalism
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.42,0:53:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,because that is the lesson
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.42,0:53:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,in that example.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.42,0:53:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Life flows equally into all
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.74,0:53:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,so we allow our unconditional love
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.74,0:53:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to support the truth of everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.74,0:53:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,including ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.74,0:53:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Our own capacity for self-healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.74,0:53:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Our own, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.74,0:53:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That I and I alone
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.74,0:53:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,have the power to make that decision
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.74,0:53:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,about whether I'm willing
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.74,0:53:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to go through the necessary inner work
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.74,0:54:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to bring about a healing
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.74,0:54:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,of this illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.58,0:54:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,To bring about a healing of the person
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.58,0:54:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,who has that illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.58,0:54:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the difference between
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.58,0:54:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,cure and heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.58,0:54:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,See, treating is treating a symptom.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.64,0:54:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Curing is curing the disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.64,0:54:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But healing is healing the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.64,0:54:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we set our intention then
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.64,0:54:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,on accomplishing that
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.64,0:54:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,which is peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.64,0:54:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The accomplishment of peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.64,0:54:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that is the end result
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.64,0:54:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.64,0:54:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The end result of healing
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.64,0:54:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is an inner tranquility.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.64,0:54:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Not an indifference
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.64,0:54:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to what happens to the body
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.64,0:54:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but a transcendence of the body
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.64,0:54:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the longer do we identify
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.64,0:54:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,as that physical thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.64,0:54:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It belongs to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.64,0:54:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's part of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.64,0:54:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is within us
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.64,0:54:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,because we realize that we are more
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.64,0:54:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,than the physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.64,0:54:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So the healing of cancer depends
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.64,0:54:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,on realizing that we are
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.64,0:55:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the one who decides
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.64,0:55:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that we are greater than
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.64,0:55:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.64,0:55:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That it is within the power of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.64,0:55:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to call forth the healer
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.64,0:55:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,within us.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.64,0:55:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And realize some of the consciousness techniques
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.64,0:55:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that we talked about today.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.64,0:55:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,See, what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.74,0:55:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,when you start to ask yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.74,0:55:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,can I heal myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.74,0:55:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this healable?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.74,0:55:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What within me needs to be healed?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.74,0:55:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,See, the cancer is only the outer
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.74,0:55:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,physical expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.74,0:55:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It still doesn't tell us, literally
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.74,0:55:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,in our own particular case
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.74,0:55:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,what needs to be healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.57,0:55:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,When I had severe diverticulitis
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.57,0:55:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,recurrent for many years
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.89,0:55:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and I would land in the hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.89,0:55:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the last time I had it
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.66,0:55:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost expired.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.81,0:55:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To really get rid of it
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.81,0:55:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,following these general principles
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.81,0:55:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, it improved
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.81,0:55:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and it got better.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.38,0:55:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And I didn't have it for some years.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.48,0:56:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And then suddenly something occurred
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.48,0:56:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.48,0:56:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and I had a recurrence
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.48,0:56:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and I had the worst attack of diverticulitis
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.48,0:56:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've ever had in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.48,0:56:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The pain was overwhelming
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.48,0:56:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and the cramping and the bleeding
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.48,0:56:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and the whole thing started all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.48,0:56:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And I asked what is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.64,0:56:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.64,0:56:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I began to question within.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.64,0:56:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And as I began to question within
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.64,0:56:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,then came to me a technique
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.64,0:56:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of going way, way back
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.64,0:56:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and discovering the exact
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.64,0:56:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and the precise meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.64,0:56:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,which lay within this particular illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.64,0:56:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And so for most of us
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.12,0:56:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,a general
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.12,0:56:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,following the general laws of healing
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.12,0:56:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,is sufficient to bring about
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.12,0:56:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,a recovery from an illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.12,0:56:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,For some of us there is
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.12,0:56:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,a very particular lesson
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.12,0:56:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that a given illness has.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.12,0:56:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A very particular message.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.12,0:56:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And the illness will get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.76,0:56:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But then something will linger on
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.76,0:56:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,or a recurrence may occur
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.76,0:56:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and the purpose of that
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.76,0:57:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,is to bring about your learning
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.76,0:57:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is a specific hidden message
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.76,0:57:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that you missed
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.76,0:57:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and please get it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.98,0:57:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The message of all of this for us then
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.98,0:57:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is that these major
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.98,0:57:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,confronts of life
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.98,0:57:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,are something
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.98,0:57:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that transforms us.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.98,0:57:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They have the power to transform.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.98,0:57:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you give the cancer within you
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.98,0:57:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,your blessing
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.98,0:57:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and you say thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.98,0:57:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,because you are giving me the power
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.98,0:57:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to transform my consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.21,0:57:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,to expand my awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.66,0:57:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,then you will be in the end
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.66,0:57:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,very thankful.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.66,0:57:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Many people who have recovered
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.66,0:57:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,from these illnesses
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.66,0:57:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,will look back and they all say
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.66,0:57:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,how grateful I am
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.66,0:57:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that that arose in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.66,0:57:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How grateful I am
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.66,0:57:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that this cancer came into my life
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.66,0:57:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and has brought me to the level
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.66,0:57:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,of awareness that I am today.
